    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense, but it sounds pretty intense. It's basically saying they can come after me for pretty much anything if something goes wrong. Are there any specific ways this could get out of hand or any sneaky details I should be looking out for in the wording?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
